Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:02.75,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:07.61,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san went out when I took\Nmy eyes off of him for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:10.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, and I had something important to say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.16,San,San,0,0,0,,I heard about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:20.06,San,San,0,0,0,,Please! No one was bothered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:23.10,San,San,0,0,0,,Neither Nagisa, me, nor Akio-san was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But society is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:29.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,As proof, I lost a position due to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:34.02,San,San,0,0,0,,But there's more than one path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:39.69,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's ready to take any path with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:42.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. She did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.61,San,San,0,0,0,,Please have faith in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:46.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.70,San,San,0,0,0,,Let's have some tea, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:52.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:57.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Also, if you don't mind, would you try the latest bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.39,San,San,0,0,0,,I'll bring some out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, my beloved daughter's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Were you out playing baseball again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:11.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Speaking of, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:14.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I called in and said I had something to say, so I'd be stopping by!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:18.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You're just here to buy bread, so don't make it so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:20.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not here to buy bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:24.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just so you know, you're not getting any discount even if you are my daughter's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll charge you double instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But Sanae's bread is a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.64,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You can buy those at the listed price.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom's standing behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:36.70,San,San,0,0,0,,So my... my bread is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:40.17,San,San,0,0,0,,...meant to be bought at the listed price?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:40.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What's the problem with selling it at the listed price?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love them-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have something important to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Oh, something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. A serious talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's time we settle this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.78,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.78,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I haven't been this excited in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why does it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:51.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm called the baker Cy Young around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.75,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Try to hit my 170 kph fastball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:58.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You do know I have a bad shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It was you who ended a game sometime ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna ask for a home run out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hit something that looks like it'll be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:12.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We'll say you win if it's not a grounder or a pop-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you really fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you win, I'll listen to what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Promise to accept whatever I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:28.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoy-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.96,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll accept anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But if I win, I'm not gonna bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ready, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Come again whenever you want to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:25.43,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,To miss the chance because of something stupid like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.73,San,San,0,0,0,,You might achieve it if you keep working for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.90,San,San,0,0,0,,How about another try for Nagisa's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.66,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.70,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I have a battle that'll determine my life waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This brat doesn't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.92,San,San,0,0,0,,Good luck to both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Try to hit my forkball that drops a whole meter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Go be a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why do we have to battle in this weather?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Weather means nothing in serious matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:32.08,San,San,0,0,0,,The bath's ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's not going to make any difference no matter how many times you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's how big the gap in strength is between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I think he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.22,San,San,0,0,0,,Knows what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I feel like he hinted it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"You're still just a kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:19.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"You're a fool to try to protect someone else."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.34,San,San,0,0,0,,You're thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.50,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san is always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.42,San,San,0,0,0,,Come, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:32.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If there's a gap in strength, then all I have left is passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll keep practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:34.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.27,San,San,0,0,0,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.40,San,San,0,0,0,,I won't stop you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.19,San,San,0,0,0,,Since, after all, it's a very important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.39,San,San,0,0,0,,I'll return to where Akio-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.45,San,San,0,0,0,,You should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:55.40,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa. You mustn't get in their way when men battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.46,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It sure rains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Is it one of those rainy autumns?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This really is the last pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:50.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.13,San,San,0,0,0,,It's a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please give Nagisa to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.77,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,He really is like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.81,San,San,0,0,0,,I knew that since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.10,San,San,0,0,0,,He's really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I was frantic to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,And I was still just a kid back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Lift your head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:10:01.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If Nagisa goes through anything sad, I'm gonna snatch her away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.42,San,San,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.16,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa is our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.97,San,San,0,0,0,,And starting today, you are our dream, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.43,San,San,0,0,0,,The happiness between you two is our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.83,San,San,0,0,0,,So please seize your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Winter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This Christmas, I spent alone with Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this year to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The day I can drink with my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've never had alcohol before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.90,San,San,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I will at least drink one cup for Dad's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:23.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I have never been gladder to have given birth to you than this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't feel that over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yay! Look at her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:45.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're sitting so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Now you're closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're completely drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's what everyone says when they're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.74,San,San,0,0,0,,What a lovey-dovey couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Does this count as lovey-dovey, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.50,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is Mom that interesting to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.67,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.17,San,San,0,0,0,,I'd like to know the truth to that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you drinking, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.43,San,San,0,0,0,,Are you interested in me, Tomoya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you, Tomoya-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A hell of a battle this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,One of them is your wife, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Answer me, Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.81,San,San,0,0,0,,This is very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae has huge boobs, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun! Why are you panicking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's proof he's interested in Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not! I'm not! I'm not! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.99,San,San,0,0,0,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I mean, I do like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,As a person, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So you do like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What the heck did I do to deserve this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Stop playing with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.05,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What's so great about being liked by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.92,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm not playing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.30,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Make up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.81,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa's very blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.56,San,San,0,0,0,,How about you, Tomoya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:25.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be happy as long as I can be with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When third semester came around, Nagisa became sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe I took you around too much over the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. I'm always like this during this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will you be able to graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Apparently that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have enough attendance even if I skip the rest of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The day of graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:15.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa sat looking out toward the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is that Mei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.80,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.34,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Are you and Nagisa-san doing well, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So-so, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is Sunohara there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:37.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan's living at the dorm, so he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.36,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The company dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.82,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Would you like his number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Sunohara. It's me, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.66,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This company's pretty unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Here, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll listen to you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right now, listen to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:04.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, whenever is best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:13.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll have to make it work with everyone else's schedule, but I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:19.31,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm right in the middle of the training period,\Nso I'll get fired if I leave the dorm without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're telling me to get fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A day wouldn't kill you, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.44,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This company's really inflexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please! Think of it as a favor for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You mean for Nagisa-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Well, if it's just one day, I think I can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:41.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm such a good guy to go through\Nall this for someone else's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.80,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You can catch me at this hour, so call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Glad you came, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:06.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Walking like this reminds me of\Nthe days we walked to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Can we enter without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I already got permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.20,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.79,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,How can you say that after seeing me for the first time in ages?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Anyone would laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I thought it was someone else at first, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.64,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:46.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Until you two came, we were playing with Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was surprised at first, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.91,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's not him without the blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.66,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Then how about we all dye it for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll get fired from work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.54,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,How are you, Furukawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm doing well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:08.30,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's really great that we were all able to gather like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:14.18,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was a shame you couldn't come to graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:18.47,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Both Rie-chan and I managed to work out our schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:23.06,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a small miracle we were all able to get together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.23,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If I were to add a word, it's a miracle of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.07,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That's exactly right, Yoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, I'm still having trouble\Nunderstanding what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.41,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.66,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:55.26,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Koumura-sensei asked the school for permission to use the campus for today's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:59.68,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I can't deny a favor asked by my last students.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:08.86,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,We will now start the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.03,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Furukawa Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.09,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Certificate of graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:35.72,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,We certify that you have met all criteria set forth by this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:06.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I experienced lots of hardship at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:12.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm shy, withdrawn, and bad at making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:17.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,After becoming a senior, I couldn't attend enough classes and had to repeat the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:25.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The spring of my second senior year, I was alone in my new class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:33.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,When I learned that there's nothing that doesn't change with the flow of time, I couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:38.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I stood helplessly at the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:44.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And, it was Tomoya-kun who gave me a push to my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:49.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since then, I've met many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:54.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,With the support of everyone here, I formed the Theater Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,At the School Festival, I was even able to stand on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:06.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But soon after that, I became ill again\Nand had to repeat my senior year again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, I thought I'd give it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wanted to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:19.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have a weak body, but I wanted to live strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:24.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The ones who gave me the strength to do that are all of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:37.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,{\fs72.9}I was in a different class from Tomoyo-san, Miyazawa-san, and Nishina-san, so I spent most of this year by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:42.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even... Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think of the school days here as very valuable ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It took me five years to graduate, but I love this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's because this is the place I worked so hard at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.62,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Congratulations for graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa's long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...long school days...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:16.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going to be married to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:25.93,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.55,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.81,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Ah... Nagisa-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.65,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Please take care of Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll be in your care, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.24,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I wish you a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We dropped off our marriage registration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okazaki Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:05.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's Nagisa's name starting today.
